divs: sighting detailsthis is a picture from a construction web cam at the shreveport\bossier port. the camera takes pic every 45 min. i just happen to look at 10:30 this morning and saw this. in the next pic it was gone. i dont know what it is but looks like a disk to me, blur from motion. if you zoom in there are three smaller object in front of it, could be birds i dont know..... thought you would be interested, i know i was. link to construction cam. *(link moved to additional evidence section below -- cms\sg.
